# This repository is release-only. Source code and local build outputs must never be committed.
*

# Repository metadata that is safe to publish.
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!README.md
!RELEASES.md

# Extra deny-list for accidental force-add attempts.
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
*.snk
*.user
*.suo
*.secrets.json
appsettings.*.json
secrets/
credentials/
tokens/

